<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #f8d7da;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #721c24;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>The recent payment for your subscription for <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> has failed.</p>
            <p>To prevent any service interruption, please update your payment method as soon as possible.</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{billingUrl}}" class="button">Update Payment Method</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Aarogentix Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>